# InventoryHub

## Overview

InventoryHub is a full-stack inventory management application built using Blazor WebAssembly and ASP.NET Core Minimal APIs.

## Features

- Product retrieval through a REST API
- JSON serialization and deserialization
- Error handling
- CORS configuration
- In-memory caching

## Technologies Used

- C#
- Blazor WebAssembly
- ASP.NET Core Minimal API
- Microsoft Copilot
- GitHub

